   --------------HAMS Control file---------------

   Waterdepth  70.0D0

   #Start Definition of Wave Frequencies
    0_inf_frequency_limits      0
    Input_frequency_type        3
    Output_frequency_type       3
    Number_of_frequencies      -10
    Minimum_frequency_Wmin    0.05D0
    Frequency_step            0.01D0
   #End Definition of Wave Frequencies

   #Start Definition of Wave Headings
    Number_of_headings          -36
    Minimum_heading           0.0D0
    Heading_step             10.0D0
   #End Definition of Wave Headings

    Reference_body_center     0.000       0.000       0.000
    Reference_body_length   1.0D0
    Wave_diffrac_solution    1
    If_remove_irr_freq       1
    Number of threads       32

   #Start Definition of Pressure and/or Elevation (PE)
    Number_of_field_points     0
   #End Definition of Pressure and/or Elevation

   ----------End HAMS Control file---------------

   Note: 
   1. A negative value for depth indicated infinite depth/deep water condition 
   2. Input_frequency_type options:
      1--deepwater wave number; 2--finite-depth wave number; 3--wave frequency; 4--wave period; 5--wave length
   3. Output_frequency_type options: same as Input_frequency_type options
   4. If_remove_irr_freq=1 indicates that the irregular frequencies will be nullified
